>immediately if I disconnect
Not sure what you expected, disconnecting before the post is allowed to propagate to all the peers. Shit is p2p after all.
The former sounds like it could be anything from fucking with the data folder/user info or not enough people browsing in general, to pick up the post and seed it for everyone else by the time you disconnect.
Ded board for dead people such as myself.
